snippet.title: Kitten Squad HD PS4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
An AMAZING twin stick shooter from the people we LOVE at PETA!  This is me starting the game up for the first time and completing the first mission.  More:

Fun facts of our animal kingdom start at https://youtu.be/-eu1YrAyJEY?t=1m30s

Gameplay starts at https://youtu.be/-eu1YrAyJEY?t=5m19s

If you'd like to take a whimsical journey to take down the evil Sheep Puncher, go here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I34haIhlC5Q


KITTEN SQUAD (INDIE) (FREE TO PLAY)
